2002-04-12 15:56  Josef Spillner <dr_maux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* dots/module.dsc.in: - keep dots version at 0.0.2 (it was
	decreased to 0.0.1 ;)

2002-04-12 15:43  Josef Spillner <dr_maux@users.sourceforge.net>

